reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These detergent sheets are delightful!
reviews.reviewText: I have never used laundry detergent sheets and was slightly reticent to try them, but did after a friend recommended them. Wow! I am so glad I did! First, the laundry sheets smell amazing. I literally pick up the package sometimes just to smell the sheets. They smell that good! Second, the laundry sheets are tiny, but pack a big punch against dirty clothes. My clothes came out clean, smelling good, and with no residue left behind. These things are magic! They also wash a lot of loads of laundry, so I find them economical, too. I will be buying them again.

reviews.reviewText: I love this! It works and it's the best smelling detergent sheets I've used. Leave clothes, blankets and towels clean, soft, and smelling good, but not too strong either.
